{
  "stem": "490.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And can-- one cannot claim that he's entitled just because somebody else has it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it's very difficult--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, entirely, it's a different system.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Today, people-- everything is-- is-- people think different.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're commercialized.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everything is-- that you-- you're entitled to everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But not in my days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In my days, you learned to be happy with the things that you have.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As long as you were able to enjoy it, you were well, and you didn't have a terrible cold or you didn't have a terrible sickness.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it was normal to grow up and to-- As a matter of fact, you had to behave, because you were depending on other people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not on relatives, or not on people who would tolerate certain things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So you didn't wait just to be told.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You knew you had to behave as a normal boy, as a normal human being.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's all what we have.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had-- we-- we became-- we went to school-- most of the-- of the boys who came to these schools, they came from out of town, from different-- different cities.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Small cities.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They sent their-- their boys there to get their education at a big-- at a big school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we developed a closeness, because the-- the studying over there was not just to make the grade.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not just to-- to-- to pass the grade.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
